{
  "id": "kaoyan-eng2-clauses",
  "name": "从句嵌套·核心难句",
  "cat": "从句",
  "desc": "定语/状语/同位语/主语从句的多层嵌套，重点训练「找主干 + 剥从句」。",
  "sentences": [
    {
      "id": "c1",
      "cat": "宾语从句+定语从句嵌套",
      "level": "较难",
      "en": "The report reveals that companies which invest heavily in employee training tend to retain the talent that their rivals desperately want.",
      "cn": "报告显示，那些在员工培训上大力投入的公司，往往能留住竞争对手求之不得的人才。",
      "parts": [
        {
          "text": "The report",
          "role": "subj",
          "note": "主句主语"
        },
        {
          "text": " ",
          "role": "plain"
        },
        {
          "text": "reveals",
          "role": "verb",
          "note": "主句谓语"
        },
        {
          "text": " ",
          "role": "plain"
        },
        {
          "text": "that",
          "role": "mark",
          "note": "宾语从句引导词"
        },
        {
          "text": " ",
          "role": "plain"
        },
        {
          "text": "companies",
          "role": "subj",
          "note": "宾语从句的主语"
        },
        {
          "text": " ",
          "role": "plain"
        },
        {
          "text": "which invest heavily in employee training",
          "role": "attr",
          "note": "定语从句1，修饰 companies"
        },
        {
          "text": " ",
          "role": "plain"
        },
        {
          "text": "tend to retain",
          "role": "verb",
          "note": "宾语从句的谓语"
        },
        {
          "text": " ",
          "role": "plain"
        },
        {
          "text": "the talent",
          "role": "obj",
          "note": "宾语"
        },
        {
          "text": " ",
          "role": "plain"
        },
        {
          "text": "that their rivals desperately want",
          "role": "attr",
          "note": "定语从句2，修饰 talent（want 后缺宾语）"
        },
        {
          "text": ".",
          "role": "plain"
        }
      ],
      "tip": "主干是 The report reveals that...（宾语从句）。宾语从句内部又套了两层定语从句：which... 修饰 companies，that their rivals... want 修饰 talent。层层剥开：先抓主干谓语 reveals，再找 that 引导的宾语从句，最后处理从句里修饰名词的两个定语从句。",
      "trap": "which 和第二个 that 都是定语从句引导词，别和引导宾语从句的 that 混淆。区分：reveals 后的 that 引导完整句子作宾语；talent 后的 that，其后 want 缺宾语，是定语从句。"
    },
    {
      "id": "c2",
      "cat": "同位语从句+让步状语从句",
      "level": "较难",
      "en": "The belief that hard work guarantees success persists even though many people discover, sometimes too late, that luck plays a role as well.",
      "cn": "「努力必定带来成功」这一信念依然根深蒂固，尽管许多人（有时为时已晚地）发现，运气同样起着作用。",
      "parts": [
        {
          "text": "The belief",
          "role": "subj",
          "note": "主句主语"
        },
        {
          "text": " ",
          "role": "plain"
        },
        {
          "text": "that hard work guarantees success",
          "role": "appos",
          "note": "同位语从句，说明 belief 的内容"
        },
        {
          "text": " ",
          "role": "plain"
        },
        {
          "text": "persists",
          "role": "verb",
          "note": "主句谓语"
        },
        {
          "text": " ",
          "role": "plain"
        },
        {
          "text": "even though",
          "role": "mark",
          "note": "让步状语从句引导词"
        },
        {
          "text": " ",
          "role": "plain"
        },
        {
          "text": "many people",
          "role": "subj",
          "note": "状语从句主语"
        },
        {
          "text": " ",
          "role": "plain"
        },
        {
          "text": "discover",
          "role": "verb",
          "note": "状语从句谓语"
        },
        {
          "text": ", sometimes too late, ",
          "role": "plain"
        },
        {
          "text": "that luck plays a role as well",
          "role": "obj",
          "note": "discover 的宾语从句"
        },
        {
          "text": ".",
          "role": "plain"
        }
      ],
      "tip": "主干 The belief persists。belief 后的 that hard work guarantees success 是同位语从句（解释 belief 的内容，that 后主谓宾完整）。even though 引导让步状语从句，从句内部又用 that 引导 discover 的宾语从句。",
      "trap": "belief 后的 that 是同位语从句不是定语从句：that 后成分完整。插入语 sometimes too late 用逗号隔开，跳过它读主干更清楚。"
    },
    {
      "id": "c3",
      "cat": "主语从句+表语从句+定语从句",
      "level": "较难",
      "en": "What surprises economists most is that consumers who claim to value privacy often hand over their personal data for trivial rewards.",
      "cn": "最让经济学家意外的是，那些声称重视隐私的消费者，往往为了微不足道的回报就交出了自己的个人数据。",
      "parts": [
        {
          "text": "What surprises economists most",
          "role": "subj",
          "note": "主语从句（What 引导，= The thing that...）"
        },
        {
          "text": " ",
          "role": "plain"
        },
        {
          "text": "is",
          "role": "verb",
          "note": "系动词"
        },
        {
          "text": " ",
          "role": "plain"
        },
        {
