        {
          "text": "consumers",
          "role": "subj",
          "note": "表语从句主语"
        },
        {
          "text": " ",
          "role": "plain"
        },
        {
          "text": "who claim to value privacy",
          "role": "attr",
          "note": "定语从句，修饰 consumers"
        },
        {
          "text": " ",
          "role": "plain"
        },
        {
          "text": "often hand over",
          "role": "verb",
          "note": "表语从句谓语"
        },
        {
          "text": " ",
          "role": "plain"
        },
        {
          "text": "their personal data",
          "role": "obj",
          "note": "宾语"
        },
        {
          "text": " ",
          "role": "plain"
        },
        {
          "text": "for trivial rewards",
          "role": "adv",
          "note": "目的/原因状语"
        },
        {
          "text": ".",
          "role": "plain"
        }
      ],
      "tip": "主干是 What... is that...。What 引导主语从句作主语，is 是系动词，that 引导表语从句。表语从句里 who claim to value privacy 是修饰 consumers 的定语从句。",
      "trap": "句首 What 不是疑问词，而是引导主语从句（相当于 The thing that）。整个 What 从句就是主语，别再去别处找主语。"
